com.facebook.rendercore

Class RenderResult<State>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.rendercore.RenderResult<State>

  • public class RenderResult<State>
extends Object
    Result from resolving a RenderState.LazyTree. A RenderResult from a previous computation will make the next computation of a new RenderState.LazyTree more efficient with internal caching.
